<div class="small"><font size="+1"><strong>SRL Daily: April 6th, 1988</strong></font></div>

<P><HR><P>
<div class="small">
<strong>TRANSACTIONS</strong>
<P>
<UL>
<LI>Magellans: Promote <strong>John Dopson</strong>, farm <strong>Tom Foley</strong>
<LI>Brewers: Place <strong>Darren Daulton</strong> on the disabled list.  Farm <strong>John Rabb</strong>.  Promote <strong>Jody Davis</strong> and <strong>Bill Pecota</strong>.
<LI>Atoms: Farm <strong>Gregg Olson</strong> and <strong>Wes Gardner</strong>.  Promote <strong>Joe Boever</strong> and <strong>Roy Smith</strong>.
</UL>
</div> 
